      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kit (Metaphors and Moonlight)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kit (Metaphors and Moonlight)" href="/user/show/42225826-kit-metaphors-and-moonlight">Kit (Metaphors and Moonlight)</a>
